description: Are you the next Grimes or Skrillex, an electronic music super-whiz that uses dozens of cables and electronics to play your shows (but no actual instruments, duh)? Alternately, are you growing your home audio system so that you can really plunge into the depths of your favorite Grimes or Skrillex tracks? With our 2 Pack of 3.5mm Auxillary Music Cables, you can keep your audio equipment organized and blaring! Stuffed with an angled-head cable and a flat cable (perfect for going under doors or behind furniture), these two cables are going to make sure that your music (whether live or recorded) booms forever, whether you are connecting a stereo to an iPod or your mixer to your other mixer to your speaker!
title: Chromo Inc. 2x Pack 3.5mm Auxiliary Cable 1 Angled and 1 Flat Audio Music Aux - Blue
